* N-Trade-A:: 5 min TF - 10 Co 20 EMA & 50 EMA [SL 5 min Candle close on Rev.] 
* Entry***Strong Trend::Price beyond VWAP SD1 band & Slanting 10, 20, 50 EMA
* PB Re-Entry::10, 20, 50 EMA 5 min | VWAP 
* Consol: >1x 10 Co 20 EMA 5 min & Price Oscillate 20 EMA & within VWAP SD1
* All Position - SL must & No Overnight
* No High leverage High loss & Reduced SL
* Trail SL::Max val of [70% of Peak profit, Swing H/L,  Prev Candle - H/L / 61% of XL]
* R/S & Profit Booking:: Recent Swing H/L | 10 min Open Range | 50, 200 MAs in 15min, 1 hr & Day | Virgin CPR
* Trend Trade:: After 11:00 am 20 EMA x 5 min | 10 min ORB Trade @ 9:20 am
* Simple PB(1x Swing), Re-Entry when Prices break consolidation and continue trend with strong candle. Complex PB (3x Swing) Re-Entry when R/S Trend Line breaks. Avoid >3x Swing correction. 
* No Counter position on Aggressive move [XL Candle]/Consol candles/5 min close
* Peak value > 3:20 pm, Especially Expiry
* Keep partial position with TL SL
* Elliot for Price Targets must concur Price Action 
* Close overnight position after 9:30 ~ 9:40am
* Never take position based on R/S alone. 10, 20, 50 EMA must concur
* Zerodha Brokerage 35.25 per trade